        6
      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Wikipedia"
      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lattingtown%2C_New_York"
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "text": "The village incorporated in 1931, and today it covers about 2,400 acres of historic marshland and residential streets.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
        9,
        23
      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Wikipedia",
        "Web source 1"
      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lattingtown%2C_New_York"
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "text": "The Underhill Burying Ground, a family cemetery, sits quietly on village land and reflects the area’s early settler heritage.",
